flowchart TD
  E[event published] --> AUDIT[write audit_log]
  AUDIT --> WU[waitUntil: run channel router]
  WU --> DEDUP{dedup key seen<br/>in cooldown window?}
  DEDUP -- yes --> SKIP[skip this recipient]
  DEDUP -- no --> CRIT{critical?}
  CRIT -- yes --> MULTI[fan out to all enabled channels<br/>email + push + in-app]
  CRIT -- no --> PREF{user prefs<br/>allow channel?}
  PREF -- no --> DROP[skip channel]
  PREF -- yes --> PRES{user has live<br/>realtime connection?}
  PRES -- yes --> INAPP[in-app live only]
  PRES -- no --> SEND[push + email]
